data.description:
PERFECT INVESTMENT OPPORTUNITY!  PROPERTY IS PRICED TO SELL!This charming 1-story single family home is  nestled within the tranquil Non HOA community in Hobe Sound, FL. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this residence offers a spacious and comfortable living experience.Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a well-designed layout that effortlessly flows from room to room. The heart of the home is the inviting kitchen, featuring elegant wooden cabinets and granite countertops. Prepare your favorite meals while enjoying the convenience of having laundry facilities right at your fingertips.Conveniently located near boat ramps, shopping, dining,  and pristine Florida beaches. The master bedroom is a true retreat, complete with a walk-in closet to cater to your storage needs and an en suite bathroom for added privacy and comfort. Imagine unwinding after a long day in your own private oasis.

One of the highlights of this home is the screened porch that leads to a splendid screened patio and pool area. Whether you're hosting gatherings or seeking relaxation, this outdoor space offers endless possibilities for enjoyment.

Situated just minutes away from the Turnpike and I-95, this location provides easy access to Wellington, Boynton Beach, and the vibrant Downtown West Palm Beach. Additionally, you'll find yourself conveniently close to stunning area beaches and three international airports, making travel and leisure a breeze.

Don't miss the chance to own a piece of paradise in this gorgeous area. Schedule your showing today and seize the opportunity to make this exceptional Hobe Sound residence your own!
